headline: Procter & Gamble vs. Clorox: Which Household Name Is Worth Watching?

headline: Is Clorox (CLX) Pricing Look Attractive After Recent Share Price Rebound
summary: If you are wondering whether Clorox is attractively priced or still has risk baked into its share price, this article walks through what the current numbers actually say about value. The stock last closed at US$113.19, with returns of 3.0% over 7 days, 14.9% over 30 days and 12.2% year to date, while the 1 year, 3 year and 5 year returns stand at a 25.6% decline, 13.1% decline and 34.7% decline respectively.
